{"id":581868,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/03/【图说天朝】无人报道：上海长宁环卫工人维权罢/","date":"2018-03-29T10:43:49Z","modified":"2018-03-29T10:45:07Z","title":"【图说天朝】无人报道：上海长宁环卫工人罢工 街头堆满垃圾","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>截至发稿时，没有任何中国媒体报道此事，相关文字、图片、视频在社交网站上遭到大量删除。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_581870\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-581870\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2.jpg 1100w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2-300x237.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2-768x607.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫2-1024x810.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_581869\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-581869\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"455\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫.jpg 1209w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫-300x260.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫-768x665.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/长宁环卫-1024x887.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">被删微博截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p>@麋鹿麋鹿Kora：<br />\n两天的转发量，让越来越多的人关注到长宁环卫工人罢工维权，新闻却仍旧未报道，环卫工人今天也是依旧在仙霞路芙蓉江路的市容管理局聚集维权，仙霞路的路边已经到处堆满垃圾，没有人解决，微博因为我连续发送关注此次时间开始扣除本用户积分，可能之后会删除或者封号，但是在此之前，环卫工人一天不放弃，我还会继续发送，让人们知道了解，很感谢转发的网友，所有评论都是站在环卫工人这一边，正如我同学所说的，没有人可以否定他们的劳动和辛劳付出，一天的早晚津贴，一个月的早晚津贴，一年的早晚津贴，几十个工人一年的早晚津贴，不是一笔小数目，他们所争取的是他们应有的权益，生活不易，背后代表的是几十个家庭。希望有人真正处理这件事，希望环卫工人维权成功。我们都太渺小，因为遇到这样的事情，无法不做一些事情，能做的就是这些，让更多的人关注事件，让有能力的人解决问题。@新浪上海 @上海长宁 @长宁绿化市容 @上海新闻<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3qcr07j20qo1bg7b1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581872\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3qcr07j20qo1bg7b1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3qcr07j20qo1bg7b1.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3qcr07j20qo1bg7b1-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3qcr07j20qo1bg7b1-575x1024.jpg 575w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3t9swbj20qo1bek1q.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581873\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3t9swbj20qo1bek1q.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3t9swbj20qo1bek1q.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3t9swbj20qo1bek1q-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk3t9swbj20qo1bek1q-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581874\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptk8z83gqj20qo0qotjm-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581875\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"475\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptkt6toitj20qo0qotin-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl1d0oej20qo1be1kx.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581882\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl1d0oej20qo1be1kx.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl1d0oej20qo1be1kx.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl1d0oej20qo1be1kx-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl1d0oej20qo1be1kx-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl4gg4oj20qo1betwg.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581883\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl4gg4oj20qo1betwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl4gg4oj20qo1betwg.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl4gg4oj20qo1betwg-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrl4gg4oj20qo1betwg-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrler0a8j20qo1beaot.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581884\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrler0a8j20qo1beaot.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"711\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrler0a8j20qo1beaot.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrler0a8j20qo1beaot-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/9e654016gy1fptrler0a8j20qo1beaot-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/2657435670/G9BzO6N2y\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@麋鹿麋鹿Kora</a>：我不知道这样做到底有没有用，可是遇到了这样的事，无法袖手旁观，所有网友的评论都是为环卫工人着想，三天了，刚刚第一次去和环卫工人聊了一下，他们不愿意录像，也是我预料之中，他们说他们马上再这样马上要被开除了，可他们所有人都还是很坚定地维护自己的权益，他们说希望有记者来报道这事件。@上海新闻 @人民日报</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_581885\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-581885\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS.jpg 1722w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS-300x168.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS-768x431.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/03/KDS-1024x574.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 